<i>So I jumped at the opportunity.</i>

05:08.074 --> 05:10.907
I can remember having a conversation
with a gentleman in my church,

05:11.010 --> 05:15.037
telling him that I was about to coach
this travel basketball team,

05:15.815 --> 05:17.783
