05:31.664 --> 05:33.154
<i>Basketball was just so much fun.</i>

05:33.266 --> 05:35.791
<i>It was a whole new world.</i>
<i>That was my playground.</i>

05:35.968 --> 05:39.597
<i>I mean, I looked forward</i>
