You don't start talking,
you never gonna play for me.

40:11.275 --> 40:14.176
You'll just be a JV guy
sitting at the end of the bench.

40:14.278 --> 40:16.075
I mean, I'm just being real with you.

40:16.180 --> 40:19.149
All right? If you can't do those little things,
how can we play?

